resources.string: So relax, be fast and have some fun !
Choose your preferred place to play
And fish to catch and try yourself in pro fisher role !
You will see fishes that swim from different parts of the screen
As soon as you will see the "Catch button" - tap it ! Because you will have very limited time for this
The higher level the less time you will have to catch the fish
Each level also have different required fishes that you need to catch to pass it
